'''Jerung''' is a moribund [[Kiranti languages|Kiranti]] language spoken in [[Nepal]]. It is mutually intelligible with [[Wambule language|Wambule]]. Dialects are Madhavpur, Balkhu-Sisneri, and Ratnawati (Sindhuli).
